[SPEAKER_06]: The designers came and changed the veneers.

860
01:20:06,466 --> 01:20:09,927
[SPEAKER_06]: The builders came and the new folk cheered.

861
01:20:11,733 --> 01:20:33,278
[SPEAKER_06]: Now they've moved closer to work in the city, to quartz countertops that made kitchens pretty, to charter schools, nannies, and drivers, and bike frames made with carbon fibers, to Starbucks lattes, artisanal breads, and articulated sleep number beds, to million dollar urban show places, and fewer and fewer black and brown faces.

862
01:20:40,578 --> 01:20:46,621
[SPEAKER_06]: They showed us their heels when they took the white flight, then they crept back in in the dead of night.

863
